    "title": "[BugFix] Correct index_map selection for transposed A matrix in MFMA Layout with `k_dim==4` and open rocm-ci for gemmsr",
    "user": {
      "login": "benenzhu",
      "id": 18651489,
      "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE4NjUxNDg5",
      "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/18651489?v=4",
      "gravatar_id": "",
